http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/10-08-96/sf1.html 199.173.162.110 19970215031633 text/html 18993
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 03:12:29 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 18:10:21 GMT
