<DOCOLDNO>IA096-001032-B003-255</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/10-08-96/st1.html 199.173.162.110 19970215032014 text/html 11818
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
