http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/13-07-96/eu1.html 199.173.162.110 19970215033406 text/html 7475
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 03:30:01 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 14:03:58 GMT
Content-length: 7288
