<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/22-06-96/am1.html 199.173.162.110 19970215034332 text/html 10199
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 03:39:30 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 14:03:59 GMT
