<DOCNO>WT09-B17-148</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA096-001032-B012-197</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/22-06-96/st1.html 199.173.162.110 19970215034558 text/html 8576
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 03:41:55 GMT
