<DOCNO>WT09-B17-230</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA096-001035-B016-261</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/11-05-96/br5.html 199.173.162.110 19970215040335 text/html 6514
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
